{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7bd15c0a-0c1d-48d3-a428-deae384993db","content":"In your `App.xaml.cs`, override `CreateWindow` and subscribe to the lifecycle events:\n\n```csharp\nprotected override Window CreateWindow(IActivationState? activationState)\n{\n    var window = base.CreateWindow(activationState);\n\n    window.Created += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Created\");\n    window.Activated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Activated\");\n    window.Deactivated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Deactivated\");\n    window.Stopped += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Stopped\");\n    window.Resumed += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Resumed\");\n    window.Destroying += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Destroying\");\n    window.Backgrounding += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Backgrounding\");\n\n    return window;\n}\n```\n\n**Typical flow:**\n\n| Transition | Event |\n|---|---|\n| App launches | `Created` → `Activated` |\n| User switches away | `Deactivated` → `Stopped` |\n| User returns | `Resumed` → `Activated` |\n| App closed | `Deactivated` → `Stopped` → `Destroying` |\n\n> **Note:** `Backgrounding` only fires on iOS/Mac Catalyst and provides a `BackgroundingEventArgs` with a `State` dictionary for saving data.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"17977803-2966-4c14-9650-f7b8acc9a98f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about subscribing to Window lifecycle events in a .NET MAUI app for debugging/logging purposes. This is a general knowledge question about .NET MAUI that I can answer directly without needing to search the codebase.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, the `Window` class exposes several lifecycle events that correspond to the app's visibility and activation states. Let me provide a concise, helpful answer.\n\nThe Window lifecycle events in .NET MAUI are:\n- Created\n- Activated\n- Deactivated\n- Stopped\n- Resumed\n- Destroying\n- Backgrounding (iOS/Mac Catalyst)\n\n\nNow I'll show a code example demonstrating how to subscribe to these events.","outputTokens":518,"requestId":"A84E:25F1DB:64BF0C:74E700:69FBE2E7"},"id":"2af284c3-d2e8-480c-9906-c47e279cac27","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:55:12.646Z","parentId":"39f4ce0c-e40f-45b3-a4d8-d3791ac2c359"}
